{
  "logNo": "224171976964",
  "title": "디지털 커팅의 한계와 그 대응 방안. 이제 모든 궁금증은 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 함께하세요.",
  "date": "2026-02-06",
  "addDate": "2026. 2. 6.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "category": "궁금증 게시판",
  "source_url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/224171976964",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c9929ac1-6728-42b2-9ca6-7c7f664c2a0d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b2e360f0-ec62-4ba1-9c5b-2632dbe5282c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-36153ce8-c1c0-4814-a263-89999841e220\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">준드(Zünd), 디지털 커팅기는 정밀도와 내구성 면에서 업계 표준으로 불리지만, 장비를 다루는 디테일에 따라 결과물의 퀄리티는 천차만별입니다. 핵심 내용을 정리해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-499d7867-674f-4058-90b1-5e899000dd12\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9b589ff3-1e26-4471-b07b-7e901d19337c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-bb84fd9d-27a5-4fed-8e6a-d563e1c4d903\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e5346d2-c68e-4f6a-846b-81e26d0a2a7c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-89307ef9-9a92-414c-b64e-10db45a8c7d1\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>디지털 커팅기(Zünd)의 한계와 완벽한 결과물을 위한 개선 가이드</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e9d5278-73dd-4ce5-b851-909f094dd0b3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224171976964/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c1da9c6-9d5c-49c9-816d-f6706580203d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-145bd460-6573-4cfd-b37f-17d40d89685f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8c87f8e8-5677-4d37-87a9-bab9e3dc7114\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 커팅기는 목형(톰슨) 없이도 복잡한 모양을 딸 수 있는 혁신적인 장비입니다. 하지만 현장에서 작업하다 보면 \"왜 단면이 지저분하지?\" 혹은 \"왜 이 종이는 안 잘릴까?\" 하는 고민이 생기기 마련이죠. 그 원인과 해결책을 짚어봅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-be1c9324-d567-45b9-8b43-c4586e18657a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224171976964/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a245c130-20c3-4d12-b523-ec017c1ed31a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65aa5dd3-1470-48eb-8a05-2e7599aac8cf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d27b9e34-31ca-4a53-a828-d5d1e44926cd\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd0a2343-6215-4e39-9f76-5227d34ab411\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-83859773-d228-40d4-a459-2c1875127c8f\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>1. 커팅이 깔끔하지 않은 이유</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b31f6da0-f03f-4a49-8467-b813c9400bfc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e7eca958-b61f-48a2-9689-ce86d377c2e0\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>(Troubleshooting)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44a7bbd1-622f-45c5-b806-92bb6cb733b7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9626a1c8-5696-469f-b5be-92fbe425bc86\" style=\"color:#555555;\">커팅 단면이 거칠거나 보푸라기가 일어나는 이유는 크게 세 가지입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf6d6f83-cc40-4383-a838-9cb066f8f35a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-be71e70a-f352-47c0-9d39-906109fd71cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>칼날(Blade)의 마모와 선택 오류</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-69fccda9-842f-4f16-9cc3-8f8a56975665\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 종이의 밀도와 두께에 맞지 않는 칼날을 사용하거나, 끝이 미세하게 마모된 칼날을 계속 사용할 때 발생합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-850fccf4-008c-425c-8cd8-e9f91d1f5010\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4418e2dc-e9df-4912-9dc4-d97bef761188\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a84edba4-1d0d-423b-937f-e74aa7d95ca2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-36f8e809-d70c-4bdd-a06e-e5fb3cbb44fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>언더레이(Underlay) 패드의 상태</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3857df6e-289c-4586-84ff-9064e4080177\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 커팅기 바닥의 매트가 너무 많이 패여 있으면 칼날이 종이를 안정적으로 받쳐주지 못해 단면이 씹히는 현상이 생깁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e683b2e-f1dc-41c9-8a75-b68e163c7c79\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-225ba4f6-ff36-4566-8a90-8164927b6c34\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ffcd5496-5b09-4eb6-ae5a-60269af13d4c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b5e0464a-1750-45b7-833a-c96bc827b9bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>진동 및 속도 제어 실패</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d2edff5c-e7c5-4d8b-ba33-2e607a96a230\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 너무 빠른 속도로 급격한 곡선을 돌 때 진동(Vibration)이 발생하면 단면에 미세한 물결무늬가 생길 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f05273bc-90a4-4649-9e10-cf925353427d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7ea9c70c-0cd6-4dd0-a960-652fd46fc4f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f94caa02-70d2-4c0d-8652-cd8d727eec9b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-752918c5-89f2-4dc1-ac08-d9a5cde532a6\" style=\"color:#0078cb;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>개선 방안</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dce59839-bfed-4d31-a648-93ec6e4df9a1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"> : &gt; 소모품 교체 주기를 철저히 관리하고, 소재의 특성에 맞춰 **오실레이팅 툴(Oscillating Tool)**의 진동 폭을 미세 조정해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b49c7004-6d43-4b7b-86eb-9f38d359aba0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-280adb83-9711-4a25-9eae-1b8851892938\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb68ca51-946e-4fdc-ab1e-95e8dba3e5a2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3d09b945-0a8f-4cc0-a7ae-dec2aae5f8c3\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>2. 종이 최대 평량과 커팅 한계</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ff8d667d-c9cb-4a70-a0bb-6c2f05b8987f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fa9abc06-b69f-4438-b08a-0d6be5a94346\" style=\"color:#555555;\">준드 커팅기는 이론적으로 매우 두꺼운 소재도 자를 수 있지만, '깔끔한 결과물'을 기준으로 본다면 한계치가 존재합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c2bdf461-8ad4-4cd2-9ffb-c60ac5106aed\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8e5c34af-7de8-4b6b-be5d-7919c6118616\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b556da95-1098-423d-991b-35aa72fc4aa6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6c6dee10-8e2e-4429-8305-399a45c3d086\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>일반적인 권장 평량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ac97b7df-040d-4fd6-b06d-171ed82e2d3e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 보통 400g/m² ~ 600g/m² 사이의 후지(두꺼운 종이)까지는 무난하게 작업 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-efc6936f-e3ad-458d-a47a-5a21e0ab1dda\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-23266030-57b4-422e-b3a5-bf2982e39930\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ac35acc-f3a6-4c6e-abc8-c10958c817f5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f33eceb8-c5cd-49f3-860b-8d475c56cf47\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>그 이상의 두께</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fed4ccea-c4e8-4533-a1d9-90d78ecfdd0e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 평량이 600g/m²를 넘어가거나 보드지(합지) 형태가 되면, 일반적인 칼날보다는 **전용 라우터(Router)**나 고주파 오실레이팅 툴을 사용해야 단면 뭉개짐을 방지할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b8f14cfa-740f-4c55-b769-0c0eaa851ae5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224171976964/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-919a7317-f61d-4f2a-bc5d-2fcdb51f473a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa79784e-3ebf-4b3e-b308-93f46057356c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7101d170-2210-48c1-b672-990a1b0736db\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0462faae-d97c-41f4-8fdd-b1d257c32701\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ad35d103-ae5f-46c8-9982-ba352ca8eb8a\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>3. 더 완벽한 결과물을 만들기 위한 조건</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a028e1da-cc78-40a1-b719-9dbfe553375d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-94ee638c-e8db-49b7-bbfd-7980ea286ec1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단순히 '잘리는 것'을 넘어 '예쁘게' 만들기 위해 반드시 체크해야 할 포인트들입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6066bc10-135b-4edc-8a49-274307d9ecae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5a45f43c-0cda-4265-a504-143b024c0bac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-38416085-e205-4be7-84a8-f178b2f132d6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70fb6701-1e7d-4e2d-933e-e991a3ee4dad\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>칼날 각도</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a7227b4-8410-4759-9155-2dad642b29fc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8b698619-5338-4660-9ae3-2073382845d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소재 두께에 따른 최적 각도(예: 60°, 45°) 선정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2c3169cd-29d4-493d-b02d-f614bfeea8dc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-27d161f4-b53c-4d31-ac94-fd4d1a19a07f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단면의 직각도 유지 및 보푸라기 방지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66173110-7ec2-4ab5-9a2b-73cd0288fee8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-25d5a069-3af8-4fdf-824e-9b887526350d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dc9478af-a279-47e5-8b72-7d6014a923a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-44ac3757-7c23-4860-b26b-5fc487032d7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>진공 압착</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-da82320e-b8bd-451f-82b7-a4cae038f295\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 강력한 진공 펌프 가동 및 마스킹 처리</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4631ad3-d5c2-4212-9af5-12994da3e63d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b0ffb527-8339-4bdb-a8bf-2252ba469348\" style=\"color:#555555;\">작업 중 소재 밀림 방지, 오차 범위 최소화</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b499010e-d6a4-4f0f-a861-1ac9a9929834\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7b6123a9-5063-48f6-85bf-7c3aa48b6489\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-774f06dc-5915-4872-9d95-3685eb0f0ea5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1ffeb145-b7ee-4054-b9db-a213d217f975\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>데이터 최적화</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-63985637-cfde-4b41-9911-d0443a562ad8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7505b46c-fcc8-4012-850f-5b66323f1e82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">베지어 곡선의 단순화 (Node 정리)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8ccec64-c3b3-4c4f-8c96-30fc047bb2a9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-96ae4d32-d725-4a0f-b248-a94791b596ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">커팅 헤드의 부드러운 이동으로 깔끔한 곡선 구현</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6043443a-36ed-43ba-8f24-b32db4a91e60\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a14d1b3b-d15c-4c48-be6f-85d3c8ae7d24\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bf748e2b-348c-41cf-8415-992a202d3da8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a78456b2-9463-49fa-8704-bdfaa4c7fb8c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>오버컷 방지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7957c62b-a2a9-4a67-b33d-7cb8283f92b4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f03b1d2a-4db8-4aaa-8f49-65e42b75d361\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소프트웨어 내 'Overcut' 값 미세 조정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-445b2c17-bca2-46eb-83f7-3ed2b2afc14a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ce8eb55a-f4cf-4284-8ad0-aed9babb9c82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">모서리 부분이 튀어나가지 않고 딱 떨어지는 마감</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a83930e-1116-4fcf-a22c-e45ce608cbfb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224171976964/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3ae8eb8-4f27-4bf9-be2d-004cb0d8a6e9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f6120332-2b0c-4685-8a05-fcc4228676ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba240b02-a31b-4636-b6e0-a5eb94bf5d6b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d1ac40e-d576-4426-8550-270b0ee2fca5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-789a78e5-8728-4bc6-8296-8efeff22180d\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>맺음말</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0ddfff3f-5f29-4e9f-8167-5a0cf69b03f7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 장비의 성능은 '디테일'에서 완성됩니다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b53b0ff0-5535-4715-8141-79fd6a3bbc5d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e186993e-b40a-4677-8a82-7e695d349567\" style=\"color:#555555;\">준드(Zünd)는 강력한 하드웨어를 가졌지만, 결국 그 결과물을 완성하는 것은 작업자의 데이터 최적화와 소모품 관리입니다. 종이의 결(Grain) 방향까지 고려해 데이터를 배치한다면, 기성 제품 못지않은 프리미엄 퀄리티를 얻을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-1dfc2876-137c-492a-9b08-5d901c7cfdc8\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d8ca4382-fed8-4a80-8d57-e1574fdf50f7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17ec336b-c336-4c62-becc-5f1ec079c577\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d00f3374-0b69-4650-a89e-c08c7679f2c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}